Sense City Can Tho Commercial Center opened on January 20, 2014, invested and built by Saigon Can Tho Trading Company Limited - a joint venture between Saigon Co.op, SCID and C.T.C with large scale. an area of over 22,000 m2 including 04 shopping and entertainment floors and 01 basement parking area with an area of 3,500 m2.  Sense City Can Tho Shopping Center integrates a variety of products and services in a modern shopping space, harmoniously arranged among the categories of fashion, cosmetics, jewelry, accessories, and furniture. family use, entertainment area and multi-regional Foodcourt dining area.  In particular, the appearance of famous domestic and foreign brands present for the first time in Can Tho and the entertainment complex for families, young people, and office workers with over 4,000 m2 for Games/Bowling is equipped with state-of-the-art equipment, a children's play area with many attractive games along with 6 international standard 2D & 3D cinemas, the first time in the Delta. Huge supermarket with all kinds of items, including food, accessories, shoes, sandals, jewelry, pharmaceuticals.... from 15k to high-end. You can almost buy anything here. The ground floor has the most mixed stores in this supermarket, selling food, ice cream, jewelry, shoes, sandals, accessories, pharmaceuticals and the supermarket's general food department. Up on the 2nd floor, everything is much more orderly as there are only clothes sold from retail stores and a section of the supermarket selling household appliances and clothes. Going to the 3rd floor is a culinary paradise when there are many restaurants here such as milk tea, fried chicken, pizza, grilled dishes, hot pot... There is also a bookstore and a play area for children. and 1 more gym. On the 4th floor is the electronic card game area for adults and the CGV cinema. The toilet here is always clean, airy and fragrant, as if I had just finished going to the toilet and a janitor would rush in to clean it immediately, so extremely clean and very satisfied. Give the supermarket 5* for satisfaction.
